{"tid":1547041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角站幫咗個妹妹既白衣先生請入","createTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T14:26:21.000Z","uid":230169,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e43c3dd24a0a3aa28d02bab273607c54ae166b6","tid":1547041,"uid":230169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"我係揹住棗紅色書包 拎住本綠色書個個妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非常感激你幫我避開個死廢老<br />\n個廢老不停逼埋黎 好彩你叫我走去你身邊<br />\n如果唔係我都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"275b3a5b3a17132d6760b5a00ecb1b58eff5f841","tid":1547041,"uid":176994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd4a00a910fee08132cda7cf518ab899ebe27242","tid":1547041,"uid":176994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"Push 到當時人睇"},{"pid":"ae7529e53bc097b4660a6e1ef6d8e84ddc1229c1","tid":1547041,"uid":290761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vAmVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vAmVU.jpg&h=305434b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門區校友街坊們過黎幫手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438c9d91adc7391017408f1a27866289348b4719","tid":1547041,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"各位關注民主自由的朋友：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自香港的示威者。<br />\n由六月初至今，反對[送中惡法]抗爭開始至今，已踏入第三個月。<br />\n過百萬位香港人多次以和平、理性、非暴力方式向政府表達我們的五個訴求。<br />\n更有7名義士的不惜犧牲自己，以死相諫，試圖喚醒當權者僅餘的良知。<br />\n可惜，在中國共產黨全面控制下的香港區政府堅拒回應市民的訴求，更借助香港警察的軍事力量，歪曲事實的假消息，無形的白色恐怖，意圖消滅所有示威者。<br />\n<br />\n我們在此向獨裁政權表明，如此卑劣性之手段絕對無法令香港人退縮或認輸，直至答應廣大市民的五個訴求。<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n二、收回至今所有反送中抗爭之暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者之控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫暴<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n香港當前面對的已經不只[送中惡法]的政治問題。<br />\n<br />\n執法：<br />\n721元朗事件，831太子事件，刻意暴力攻擊示威者，濫捕。<br />\n警權之大，前所未見，己達至軍政府統治下的戒嚴狀態。<br />\n<br />\n司法：<br />\n為達到中共維穩目標，公然遣背法律公平公正的原則。<br />\n不斷政治檢控示威者/區議員/立法會議員。<br />\n<br />\n行政：<br />\n放仼警方使用過份武力，更加直接表明支持。<br />\n散播白色恐怖，打壓一齊反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n人道：<br />\n凌辱及暴力對待被捕人未，包括性暴力。<br />\n故意攻擊救援人員，阻止救援人員為傷者進行急救。<br />\n<br />\n中共勢力已全面入侵香港，徹底違反《中英聯合聲明》所承諾的一國兩制。<br />\n解決當前的政治問題已不能令千瘡百孔的香港重回正軌，我們必須重新建設整個政府體制，實現民選政府。<br />\n<br />\n為對抗如此醜惡的政權，香港人經歷了無數血與汗的洗禮，然而面前的高牆已非我們可以獨自打破。<br />\n所以，我們在在呼籲各支持民主自由的國家/組織/市民積極介入，以不同的方式協助香港對抗極權國家，或制裁支持極權的人士。<br />\n<br />\n包括：<br />\n凍結個別人士在國外的資產，以經濟方式懲罰<br />\n禁止個別人士及其親屬入境，以外交方式懲罪<br />\n派員協助香港人籌組新民選政府<br />\n給予政治庇護/公民身份<br />\n<br />\n不自由，毋寧死。香港人定必採取一切可行手段，使香港邁進成為民主、自由、公義的社會。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">以上參考過往的宣言</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[認真]  既然要國際支援，點解唔講出嚟？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知有冇用，但我覺得要向外國講出我地嘅要求同現況，有冇可能係星期日試吓？</span>"},{"pid":"d7cbe417f8234e7603620e76814f60e07fdc673c","tid":1547041,"uid":293490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f7353408fefbeb1863a13a92376759fc504ad9","tid":1547041,"uid":176994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2392b81eb700bf36e33de086b01654b2875a16cd","tid":1547041,"uid":230169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"da06b43a1081593ad21402fefb268e324c43a8ad","tid":1547041,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a57dfbb03774b5ff833e877926c46fb3dea0d45d","tid":1547041,"uid":176994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:02:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d1284663c8e2ee0ef0ed3e6b0f3d54bfb060f86","tid":1547041,"uid":155224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"咩事?"},{"pid":"936beb8e907688c3c50ed35a1e55d36ccaddc605","tid":1547041,"uid":176994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持警察<br />\n吞槍自殺</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"21ac9746bc21045275a77a127fc051ed373569e6","tid":1547041,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"564ad22e27989487158772bb6c3bb4124c102d6e","tid":1547041,"uid":176994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港人<br />\n加油</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a2c6f258fd93efdbd1